.introduction
  %h1
    Available For Hire
    
  %p
    If you're looking for some local Ruby talent to 
    help with your project, or just hang around drinking beers
    all day, you could do worse than starting with this list.

  - if current_user
    %br
    - unless current_user.for_hire
      %p= "If you are a Ruby developer, #{link_to 'click here', :action => 'new'} to add a listing."
    - else
      %p= "You already have a \"For Hire\" entry.  You may edit it #{link_to 'here', :action => 'edit'}."
    

.hires
  %ul
    = render :partial => 'for_hire', :collection => @for_hires
